service.name: Language, Literacy and Numeracy Supplement
service.description: The Language, Literacy and Numeracy Supplement (LLNS) may be available to customers who participate in Skills for Education and Employment (SEE).  The LLNS provides financial assistance for job seekers who want to improve their language, literacy and numeracy skills as part of their plan to return to work. This assistance is to enable job seekers undertaking SEE to meet the additional costs associated with attendance and provides an incentive for them to participate in the program.
